doc.after: A total of 77 DC-9 aircraft (all variants) were in commercial service as of January 2014, including USA Jet Airlines (10), Insel Air (7), Everts Air Cargo (3), Aeronaves TSM (6), Aserca Airlines (4), LASER Airlines (3), Fly SAX (2), African Express Airways (2), Fly540 (2), and other operators with fewer aircraft.[16]
